forest where Tranquill live, there is
a peaceful place where there is no war.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(521,17,9,'Males swing their head plumage to
threaten opponents. The femalesí flying
abilities surpass those of the males.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(521,18,9,'Males have plumage on their heads.
They will never let themselves feel close
to anyone other than their Trainers.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(522,17,9,'Its mane shines when it discharges
electricity. They use their flashing
manes to communicate with one another.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(522,18,9,'When thunderclouds cover the sky,
it will appear. It can catch lightning
with its mane and store the electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(523,17,9,'They have lightning-like movements.
When Zebstrika run at full speed,
the sound of thunder reverberates.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(523,18,9,'This ill-tempered PokÈmon is dangerous
because when itís angry, it shoots
lightning from its mane in all directions.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(524,17,9,'Its ear is hexagonal in shape.
Compressed underground,
its body is as hard as steel.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(524,18,9,'They were discovered a hundred years
ago in an earthquake fissure. Inside
each one is an energy core.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(525,17,9,'When it overflows with power,
the orange crystal on its body glows.
It looks for underground water in caves.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(525,18,9,'Because its energy was too great to be
contained, the energy leaked and formed
orange crystals.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(526,17,9,'Compressing the energy from its
internal core lets it fire off an attack
capable of blowing away a mountain.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(526,18,9,'The solar energy absorbed by its bodyís
orange crystals is magnified internally
and fired from its mouth.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(527,17,9,'Its habitat is dark forests and caves.
It emits ultrasonic waves from its
nose to learn about its surroundings.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(527,18,9,'Suction from its nostrils enables it to
stick to cave walls during sleep. It
leaves a heart-shaped mark behind.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(528,17,9,'It emits sound waves of various
frequencies from its nose, including
some powerful enough to destroy rocks.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(528,18,9,'Anyone who comes into contact with the
ultrasonic waves emitted by a courting
male experiences a positive mood shift.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(529,17,9,'It can dig through the ground
at a speed of 30 mph. It could give
a car running aboveground a good race.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(529,18,9,'It makes its way swiftly through the soil
by putting both claws together and
rotating at high speed.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(530,17,9,'It can help in tunnel construction.
Its drill has evolved into steel strong
enough to bore through iron plates.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(530,18,9,'More than 300 feet below the surface,
they build mazelike nests. Their activity
can be destructive to subway tunnels.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(531,17,9,'It touches others with the feelers on
its ears, using the sound of their
heartbeats to tell how they are feeling.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(531,18,9,'Its auditory sense is astounding. It has
a radarlike ability to understand its
surroundings through slight sounds.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(532,17,9,'It fights by swinging a piece of lumber
around. It is close to evolving when it
can handle the lumber without difficulty.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(532,18,9,'These PokÈmon appear at building
sites and help out with construction.
They always carry squared logs.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(533,17,9,'This PokÈmon is so muscular and strongly
built that even a group of wrestlers
could not make it budge an inch.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(533,18,9,'They strengthen their bodies by
carrying steel beams. They show off
their big muscles to their friends.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(534,17,9,'It is thought that Conkeldurr taught
humans how to make concrete more
than 2,000 years ago.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(534,18,9,'They use concrete pillars as walking
canes. They know moves that enable them
to swing the pillars freely in battle.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(535,17,9,'They warn others of danger by
vibrating their cheeks to create
a high-pitched sound.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(535,18,9,'By vibrating its cheeks, it emits sound
waves imperceptible to humans. It uses
the rhythm of these sounds to talk.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(536,17,9,'When they vibrate the bumps on their
heads, they can make waves in water
or earthquake-like vibrations on land.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(536,18,9,'It lives in the water and on land.
It uses its long, sticky tongue
to capture prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(537,17,9,'They shoot paralyzing liquid from their
head bumps. They use vibration to hurt
their opponents.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(537,18,9,'It increases the power of its punches by
vibrating the bumps on its fists. It can
turn a boulder to rubble with one punch.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(538,17,9,'When it tightens its belt, it becomes
stronger. Wild Throh use vines to weave
their own belts.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(538,18,9,'When they encounter foes bigger than
themselves, they try to throw them.
They always travel in packs of five.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(539,17,9,'The sound of Sawk punching boulders
and trees can be heard all the way from
the mountains where they train.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(539,18,9,'Tying their belts gets them pumped and
makes their punches more destructive.
Disturbing their training angers them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(540,17,9,'Leavanny dress it in clothes they made
for it when it hatched. It hides its head
in its hood while it is sleeping.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(540,18,9,'This PokÈmon makes clothes for itself.
It chews up leaves and sews them with
sticky thread extruded from its mouth.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(541,17,9,'Forests where Swadloon live have superb
foliage because the nutrients they make
from fallen leaves nourish the plant life.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(541,18,9,'It protects itself from the cold
by wrapping up in leaves. It stays on
the move, eating leaves in forests.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(542,17,9,'Upon finding a small PokÈmon, it weaves
clothing for it from leaves, using the
cutters on its arms and sticky silk.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(542,18,9,'It keeps its eggs warm with heat from
fermenting leaves. It also uses leaves
to make warm wrappings for Sewaddle.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(543,17,9,'Its bite injects a potent poison, enough
to paralyze large bird PokÈmon that try
to prey on it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(543,18,9,'It discovers what is going on around it
by using the feelers on its head and tail.
It is brutally aggressive.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(544,17,9,'Protected by a hard shell, it spins
its body like a wheel and crashes
furiously into its enemies.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(544,18,9,'It is usually motionless, but when
attacked, it rotates at high speed and
then crashes into its opponent.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(545,17,9,'With quick movements, it chases down
its foes, attacking relentlessly with
its horns until it prevails.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(545,18,9,'Highly aggressive, it uses the claws
near its neck to dig into its opponents
and poison them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(546,17,9,'When attacked, it escapes by shooting
cotton from its body. The cotton serves
as a decoy to distract the attacker.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(546,18,9,'They go wherever the wind takes them.
On rainy days, their bodies are heavier,
so they take shelter beneath big trees.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(547,17,9,'Like the wind, it can slip through any
gap, no matter how small. It leaves
balls of white fluff behind.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(547,18,9,'Riding whirlwinds, they appear.
These PokÈmon sneak through gaps into
houses and cause all sorts of mischief.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(548,17,9,'The leaves on its head are very bitter.
Eating one of these leaves is known
to refresh a tired body.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(548,18,9,'Since they prefer moist, nutrient-rich
soil, the areas where Petilil live are
known to be good for growing plants.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(549,17,9,'Even veteran Trainers face a challenge
in getting its beautiful flower to bloom.
This PokÈmon is popular with celebrities.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(549,18,9,'The fragrance of the garland on its head
has a relaxing effect. It withers if a
Trainer does not take good care of it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(550,17,9,'Red and blue Basculin get along so
poorly, theyíll start fighting instantly.
These PokÈmon are very hostile.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(550,18,9,'Red and blue Basculin usually do not
get along, but sometimes members of one
school mingle with the otherís school.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(551,17,9,'They live buried in the sands of the
desert. The sun-warmed sands prevent
their body temperature from dropping.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(551,18,9,'It moves along below the sandís surface,
except for its nose and eyes. A dark
membrane shields its eyes from the sun.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(552,17,9,'They live in groups of a few individuals.
Protective membranes shield their eyes
from sandstorms.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(552,18,9,'The special membrane covering its eyes
can sense the heat of objects, so it can
see its surroundings even in darkness.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(553,17,9,'They never allow prey to escape.
Their jaws are so powerful, they can
crush the body of an automobile.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(553,18,9,'It can expand the focus of its eyes,
enabling it to see objects in the far
distance as if it were using binoculars.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(554,17,9,'When its internal fire is burning, it
cannot calm down and it runs around.
When the fire diminishes, it falls asleep.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(554,18,9,'Darumakaís droppings are hot, so
people used to put them in their
clothes to keep themselves warm.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(555,17,9,'Its internal fire burns at 2,500∞ F,
making enough power that it can
destroy a dump truck with one punch.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(555,18,9,'When weakened in battle, it transforms
into a stone statue. Then it sharpens
its mind and fights on mentally.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(556,17,9,'It uses an up-tempo song and dance
to drive away the bird PokÈmon that
prey on its flower seeds.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(556,18,9,'Arid regions are their habitat.
They move rhythmically, making
a sound similar to maracas.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(557,17,9,'This PokÈmon can easily melt holes in
hard rocks with a liquid secreted from
its mouth.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(557,18,9,'It makes a hole in a suitable rock. If
that rock breaks, the PokÈmon remains
agitated until it locates a replacement.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(558,17,9,'Competing for territory, Crustle
fight viciously. The one whose boulder
is broken is the loser of the battle.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(558,18,9,'It possesses legs of enormous strength,
enabling it to carry heavy slabs for many
days, even when crossing arid land.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(559,17,9,'Its skin has a rubbery elasticity, so
it can reduce damage by defensively
pulling its skin up to its neck.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(559,18,9,'It immediately headbutts anyone that
makes eye contact with it. Its skull is
massively thick.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(560,17,9,'Groups of them beat up anything
that enters their territory. Each can
spit acidic liquid from its mouth.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(560,18,9,'It can smash concrete blocks with its
kicking attacks. The one with the biggest
crest is the group leader.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(561,17,9,'They never vary the route they fly,
because their memories of guarding
an ancient city remain steadfast.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(561,18,9,'The guardians of an ancient city, they
use their psychic power to attack
enemies that invade their territory.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(562,17,9,'Each of them carries a mask that used
to be its face when it was human.
Sometimes they look at it and cry.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(562,18,9,'These PokÈmon arose from the spirits of
people interred in graves in past ages.
Each retains memories of its former life.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(563,17,9,'It has been said that they swallow those
who get too close and turn them into
mummies. They like to eat gold nuggets.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(563,18,9,'They pretend to be elaborate coffins
to teach lessons to grave robbers.
Their bodies are covered in pure gold.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(564,17,9,'Restored from a fossil, this PokÈmon
can dive to depths beyond half a mile.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(564,18,9,'About 100 million years ago, these
PokÈmon swam in oceans. It is thought
they also went on land to attack prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(565,17,9,'They can live both in the ocean and on
land. A slap from one of them is enough
to open a hole in the bottom of a tanker.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(565,18,9,'Incredible jaw strength enables them
to chew up steel beams and rocks
along with their prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(566,17,9,'Said to be an ancestor of bird PokÈmon,
they were unable to fly and moved about
by hopping from one branch to another.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(566,18,9,'Revived from a fossil, this PokÈmon
is thought to be the ancestor of all
bird PokÈmon.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(567,17,9,'They are intelligent and will cooperate
to catch prey. From the ground, they
use a running start to take flight.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(567,18,9,'It runs better than it flies.
It catches prey by running at speeds
comparable to those of an automobile.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(568,17,9,'Inhaling the gas they belch will make
you sleep for a week. They prefer
unsanitary places.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(568,18,9,'The combination of garbage bags and
industrial waste caused the chemical
reaction that created this PokÈmon.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(569,17,9,'It clenches opponents with its left arm
and finishes them off with foul-smelling
poison gas belched from its mouth.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(569,18,9,'They absorb garbage and make it part
of their bodies. They shoot a poisonous
liquid from their right-hand fingertips.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(570,17,9,'It changes into the forms of others
to surprise them. Apparently, it
often transforms into a silent child.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(570,18,9,'To protect themselves from danger,
they hide their true identities by
transforming into people and PokÈmon.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(571,17,9,'Bonds between these PokÈmon are very
strong. It protects the safety of its
pack by tricking its opponents.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(571,18,9,'Each has the ability to fool a large
group of people simultaneously. They
protect their lair with illusory scenery.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(572,17,9,'They greet one another by rubbing each
other with their tails, which are always
kept well groomed and clean.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(572,18,9,'These PokÈmon prefer a tidy habitat.
They are always sweeping and dusting,
using their tails as brooms.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(573,17,9,'Their white fur is coated in a special oil
that makes it easy for them to
deflect attacks.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(573,18,9,'Their white fur feels amazing to touch.
Their fur repels dust and prevents
static electricity from building up.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(574,17,9,'Their ribbonlike feelers increase their
psychic power. They are always staring
at something.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(574,18,9,'They intently observe both Trainers and
PokÈmon. Apparently, they are looking
at something that only Gothita can see.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(575,17,9,'They use hypnosis to control people and
PokÈmon. Tales of Gothorita leading
people astray are told in every corner.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(575,18,9,'Starlight is the source of their power.
At night, they mark star positions by
using psychic power to float stones.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(576,17,9,'Starry skies thousands of light-years
away are visible in the space distorted
by their intense psychic power.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(576,18,9,'They can predict the future from the
placement and movement of the stars.
They can see Trainersí life spans.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(577,17,9,'They drive away attackers by unleashing
psychic power. They can use telepathy
to talk with others.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(577,18,9,'Because their bodies are enveloped
in a special liquid, they can survive
in any environment.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(578,17,9,'Since they have two divided brains,
at times they suddenly try to take two
different actions at once.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(578,18,9,'When their brains, now divided in two,
are thinking the same thoughts, these
PokÈmon exhibit their maximum power.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(579,17,9,'When Reuniclus shake hands, a network
forms between their brains, increasing
their psychic power.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(579,18,9,'These remarkably intelligent PokÈmon
fight by controlling arms that can
grip with rock-crushing power.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(580,17,9,'These bird PokÈmon are excellent divers.
They swim around in the water eating
their favorite food--peat moss.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(580,18,9,'When attacked, it uses its feathers
to splash water, escaping under cover
of the spray.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(581,17,9,'Swanna start to dance at dusk.
The one dancing in the middle is
the leader of the flock.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(581,18,9,'It administers sharp, powerful pecks
with its bill. It whips its long neck to
deliver forceful repeated strikes.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(582,17,9,'The temperature of their breath
is -58∞ F. They create snow crystals and
make snow fall in the areas around them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(582,18,9,'This PokÈmon formed from icicles
bathed in energy from the morning sun.
It sleeps buried in snow.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(583,17,9,'Snowy mountains are this PokÈmonís
habitat. During an ancient ice age, they
moved to southern areas.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(583,18,9,'It conceals itself from enemy eyes
by creating many small ice particles
and hiding among them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(584,17,9,'Swallowing large amounts of water, they
make snow clouds inside their bodies and
attack their foes with violent blizzards.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(584,18,9,'If both heads get angry simultaneously,
this PokÈmon expels a blizzard, burying
everything in snow.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(585,17,9,'The color and scent of their fur changes
to match the mountain grass. When they
sense hostility, they hide in the grass.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(585,18,9,'The turning of the seasons changes the
color and scent of this PokÈmonís fur.
People use it to mark the seasons.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(586,17,9,'They migrate according to the seasons.
People can tell the season by looking at
Sawsbuckís horns.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(586,18,9,'The plants growing on its horns change
according to the season. The leaders of
the herd possess magnificent horns.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(587,17,9,'The energy made in its cheeksí electric
pouches is stored inside its membrane
and released while it is gliding.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(587,18,9,'They live on treetops and glide using
the inside of a cape-like membrane
while discharging electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(588,17,9,'These mysterious PokÈmon evolve when
they receive electrical stimulation while
they are in the same place as Shelmet.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(588,18,9,'When they feel threatened, they spit
an acidic liquid to drive attackers away.
This PokÈmon targets Shelmet.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(589,17,9,'They fly around at high speed, striking
with their pointed spears. Even when in
trouble, they face opponents bravely.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(589,18,9,'These PokÈmon evolve by wearing the
shell covering of a Shelmet. The steel
armor protects their whole body.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(590,17,9,'It lures people in with its PokÈ Ball
pattern, then releases poison spores.
Why it resembles a PokÈ Ball is unknown.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(590,18,9,'For some reason, this PokÈmon resembles
a PokÈ Ball. They release poison spores
to repel those who try to catch them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(591,17,9,'It lures prey close by dancing and
waving its arm caps, which resemble
PokÈ Balls, in a swaying motion.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(591,18,9,'They show off their PokÈ Ball caps to
lure prey, but very few PokÈmon are
fooled by this.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(592,17,9,'With its thin, veil-like arms wrapped
around the body of its opponent,
it sinks to the ocean floor.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(592,18,9,'They paralyze prey with poison,
then drag them down to their lairs,
five miles below the surface.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(593,17,9,'The fate of the ships and crew that
wander into Jellicentís habitat:
all sunken, all lost, all vanished.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(593,18,9,'They propel themselves by expelling
absorbed seawater from their bodies.
Their favorite food is life energy.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(594,17,9,'The special membrane enveloping
Alomomola has the ability to heal wounds.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(594,18,9,'Floating in the open sea is how they live.
When they find a wounded PokÈmon,
they embrace it and bring it to shore.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(595,17,9,'Joltik that live in cities have learned
a technique for sucking electricity
from the outlets in houses.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(595,18,9,'They attach themselves to large-bodied
PokÈmon and absorb static electricity,
which they store in an electric pouch.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(596,17,9,'When attacked, they create an
electric barrier by spitting out
many electrically charged threads.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(596,18,9,'They employ an electrically charged web
to trap their prey. While it is immobilized
by shock, they leisurely consume it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(597,17,9,'When threatened, it attacks by
shooting a barrage of spikes, which gives
it a chance to escape by rolling away.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(597,18,9,'They stick their spikes into cave
walls and absorb the minerals
they find in the rock.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(598,17,9,'It fights by swinging around its three
spiky feelers. A hit from these steel
spikes can reduce a boulder to rubble.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(598,18,9,'They attach themselves to cave
ceilings, firing steel spikes at targets
passing beneath them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(599,17,9,'The two minigears that mesh together
are predetermined. Each will rebound
from other minigears without meshing.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(599,18,9,'Interlocking two bodies and
spinning around generates
the energy they need to live.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(600,17,9,'By changing the direction in which it
rotates, it communicates its feelings to
others. When angry, it rotates faster.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(600,18,9,'Spinning minigears are rotated at high
speed and repeatedly fired away. It is
dangerous if the gears donít return.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(601,17,9,'Its red core functions as an energy
tank. It fires the charged energy
through its spikes into an area.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(601,18,9,'The gear with the red core is
rotated at high speed for a
rapid energy charge.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(602,17,9,'While one alone doesnít have much power,
a chain of many Tynamo can be as
powerful as lightning.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(602,18,9,'These PokÈmon move in schools. They
have an electricity-generating organ, so
they discharge electricity if in danger.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(603,17,9,'They coil around foes and shock them
with electricity-generating organs that
seem simply to be circular patterns.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(603,18,9,'These PokÈmon have a big appetite.
When they spot their prey, they attack
it and paralyze it with electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(604,17,9,'They crawl out of the ocean using their
arms. They will attack prey on shore and
immediately drag it into the ocean.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(604,18,9,'With their sucker mouths, they
suck in prey. Then they use their fangs
to shock the prey with electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(605,17,9,'It uses its strong psychic power
to squeeze its opponentís brain,
causing unendurable headaches.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(605,18,9,'This PokÈmon had never been seen until
it appeared from far in the desert
50 years ago.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(606,17,9,'It can manipulate an opponentís memory.
Apparently, it communicates by flashing
its three different-colored fingers.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(606,18,9,'It uses psychic power
to control an opponentís brain
and tamper with its memories.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(607,17,9,'Litwick shines a light that absorbs the
life energy of people and PokÈmon,
which becomes the fuel that it burns.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(607,18,9,'While shining a light and pretending
to be a guide, it leeches off the life
force of any who follow it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(608,17,9,'This ominous PokÈmon is feared.
Through cities it wanders, searching
for the spirits of the fallen.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(608,18,9,'It arrives near the moment of death
and steals spirit from the body.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(609,17,9,'It absorbs a spirit, which it then burns.
By waving the flames on its arms,
it puts its foes into a hypnotic trance.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(609,18,9,'Being consumed in Chandelureís flame
burns up the spirit, leaving the
body behind.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(610,17,9,'They use their tusks to crush the
berries they eat. Repeated regrowth
makes their tusks strong and sharp.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(610,18,9,'They mark their territory by leaving
gashes in trees with their tusks. If a
tusk breaks, a new one grows in quickly.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(611,17,9,'Since a broken tusk will not grow back,
they diligently sharpen their tusks on
river rocks after theyíve been fighting.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(611,18,9,'Their tusks can shatter rocks.
Territory battles between Fraxure
can be intensely violent.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(612,17,9,'They are kind but can be relentless
when defending territory. They challenge
foes with tusks that can cut steel.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(612,18,9,'Their sturdy tusks will stay sharp even
if used to cut steel beams. These
PokÈmon are covered in hard armor.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(613,17,9,'When it is not feeling well, its mucus
gets watery and the power of its
Ice-type moves decreases.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(613,18,9,'Its nose is always running. It sniffs the
snot back up because the mucus
provides the raw material for its moves.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(614,17,9,'It can make its breath freeze at will.
Very able in the water, it swims around
in northern seas and catches prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(614,18,9,'It freezes its breath to create
fangs and claws of ice to fight with.
Cold northern areas are its habitat.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(615,17,9,'When its body temperature goes up, it
turns into steam and vanishes. When its
temperature lowers, it returns to ice.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(615,18,9,'They are born in snow clouds.
They use chains made of
ice crystals to capture prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(616,17,9,'When attacked, it defends itself by
closing the lid of its shell. It can spit
a sticky, poisonous liquid.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(616,18,9,'It evolves when bathed in an
electric-like energy along with
Karrablast. The reason is still unknown.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(617,17,9,'When its body dries out, it weakens.
So, to prevent dehydration, it wraps
itself in many layers of thin membrane.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(617,18,9,'Having removed its heavy shell,
it becomes very light and can fight
with ninja-like movements.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(618,17,9,'Its skin is very hard, so it is unhurt
even if stepped on by sumo wrestlers.
It smiles when transmitting electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(618,18,9,'It conceals itself in the mud of the
seashore. Then it waits. When prey touch
it, it delivers a jolt of electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(619,17,9,'In fights, they dominate with onslaughts
of flowing, continuous attacks. With
their sharp claws, they cut enemies.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(619,18,9,'They have mastered elegant combos.
As they concentrate, their battle moves
become swifter and more precise.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(620,17,9,'It wields the fur on its arms like a whip.
Its arm attacks come with such rapidity
that they cannot even be seen.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(620,18,9,'They use the long fur on their arms
as a whip to strike their opponents.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(621,17,9,'It warms its body by absorbing sunlight
with its wings. When its body temperature
falls, it can no longer move.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(621,18,9,'It races through narrow caves, using
its sharp claws to catch prey. The skin
on its face is harder than a rock.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(622,17,9,'The energy that burns inside it
enables it to move, but no one has yet
been able to identify this energy.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(622,18,9,'These PokÈmon are thought to have been
created by the science of an ancient
and mysterious civilization.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(623,17,9,'It flies across the sky at Mach speeds.
Removing the seal on its chest makes
its internal energy go out of control.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(623,18,9,'It is said that Golurk were ordered
to protect people and PokÈmon
by the ancient people who made them.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(624,17,9,'Blades comprise this PokÈmonís entire
body. If battling dulls the blades, it
sharpens them on stones by the river.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(624,18,9,'They fight at Bisharpís command.
They cling to their prey and inflict
damage by sinking their blades into it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(625,17,9,'It leads a group of Pawniard.
It battles to become the boss, but will
be driven from the group if it loses.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(625,18,9,'Bisharp pursues prey in the company of a
large group of Pawniard. Then Bisharp
finishes off the prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(626,17,9,'Their fluffy fur absorbs damage,
even if they strike foes with a
fierce headbutt.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(626,18,9,'They charge wildly and headbutt
everything. Their headbutts have enough
destructive force to derail a train.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(627,17,9,'They crush berries with their talons.
They bravely stand up to any opponent,
no matter how strong it is.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(627,18,9,'They will challenge anything, even strong
opponents, without fear. Their frequent
fights help them become stronger.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(628,17,9,'They fight for their friends without any
thought about danger to themselves.
One can carry a car while flying.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(628,18,9,'The more scars they have, the more
respect these brave soldiers of the sky 
get from their peers.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(629,17,9,'Its wings are too tiny to allow it to fly.
As the time approaches for it to evolve,
it discards the bones it was wearing.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(629,18,9,'They tend to guard their posteriors
with suitable bones they have found.
They pursue weak PokÈmon.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(630,17,9,'It makes a nest out of bones it finds.
It grabs weakened prey in its talons
and hauls it to its nest of bones.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(630,18,9,'Watching from the sky, they swoop to
strike weakened PokÈmon on the ground.
They decorate themselves with bones.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(631,17,9,'It breathes through a hole in its tail
while it burns with an internal fire.
Durant is its prey.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(631,18,9,'Using their very hot, flame-covered
tongues, they burn through Durantís
steel bodies and consume their insides.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(632,17,9,'They attack in groups, covering
themselves in steel armor to
protect themselves from Heatmor.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(632,18,9,'Durant dig nests in mountains.
They build their complicated,
interconnected tunnels into mazes.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(633,17,9,'It tends to bite everything, and it
is not a picky eater. Approaching it
carelessly is dangerous.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(633,18,9,'They cannot see, so they tackle and bite
to learn about their surroundings.
Their bodies are covered in wounds.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(634,17,9,'After it has eaten up all the food in
its territory, it moves to another
area. Its two heads do not get along.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(634,18,9,'Since their two heads do not get along
and compete with each other for food,
they always eat too much.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(635,17,9,'This brutal PokÈmon travels the skies on
its six wings. Anything that moves seems
like a foe to it, triggering its attack.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(635,18,9,'The heads on their arms do not have
brains. They use all three heads to
consume and destroy everything.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(636,17,9,'This PokÈmon was believed to have
been born from the sun. When it evolves,
its entire body is engulfed in flames.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(636,18,9,'The base of volcanoes is where they make
their homes. They shoot fire from their
five horns to repel attacking enemies.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(637,17,9,'When volcanic ash darkened the
atmosphere, it is said that Volcaronaís
fire provided a replacement for the sun.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(637,18,9,'A sea of fire engulfs the surroundings
of their battles, since they use their
six wings to scatter their ember scales.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(638,17,9,'This legendary PokÈmon battled against
humans to protect PokÈmon.
Its personality is calm and composed.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(638,18,9,'It has a body and heart of steel.
Its glare is sufficient to make even
an unruly PokÈmon obey it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(639,17,9,'This PokÈmon came to the defense of
PokÈmon that had lost their homes in
a war among humans.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(639,18,9,'Its charge is strong enough to break
through a giant castle wall in one blow.
This PokÈmon is spoken of in legends.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(640,17,9,'This PokÈmon fought humans in order
to protect its friends. Legends about it
continue to be passed down.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(640,18,9,'Its head sprouts horns as sharp as
blades. Using whirlwind-like movements,
it confounds and swiftly cuts opponents.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(641,17,9,'The lower half of its body is wrapped in
a cloud of energy. It zooms through
the sky at 200 mph.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(641,18,9,'Tornadus expels massive energy from its
tail, causing severe storms. Its power
is great enough to blow houses away.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(642,17,9,'Countless charred remains mar the
landscape of places through which
Thundurus has passed.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(642,18,9,'The spikes on its tail discharge immense
bolts of lightning. It flies around the
Unova region firing off lightning bolts.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(643,17,9,'This PokÈmon appears in legends.
It sends flames into the air from its
tail, burning up everything around it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(643,18,9,'When Reshiramís tail flares, the
heat energy moves the atmosphere
and changes the worldís weather.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(644,17,9,'Concealing itself in lightning clouds,
it flies throughout the Unova region.
It creates electricity in its tail.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(644,18,9,'This PokÈmon appears in legends.
In its tail, it has a giant generator
that creates electricity.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(645,17,9,'Lands visited by Landorus grant such
bountiful crops that it has been hailed
as ìThe Guardian of the Fields.î');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(645,18,9,'The energy that comes pouring from its
tail increases the nutrition in the soil,
making crops grow to great size.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(646,17,9,'It generates a powerful, freezing
energy inside itself, but its body became
frozen when the energy leaked out.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(646,18,9,'It can produce ultracold air.
Its body is frozen.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(647,17,9,'By blasting water from its hooves, it can
glide across water. It excels at using
leg moves while battling.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(647,18,9,'It crosses the world, running over
the surfaces of oceans and rivers.
It appears at scenic waterfronts.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(648,17,9,'Its melodies are sung with a special
vocalization method that can control
the feelings of those who hear it.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(648,18,9,'Many famous songs have been inspired
by the melodies that Meloetta plays.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(649,17,9,'Over 300 million years ago, it was feared
as the strongest of hunters.
It has been modified by Team Plasma.');
INSERT INTO pokemon_species_flavor_text VALUES(649,18,9,'This ancient bug PokÈmon was altered
by Team Plasma. They upgraded the
cannon on its back.');